Get a list of unique sectors

Source: R/key_func.R
get_list_of_sectors.Rd

These include which sector the underlying data belongs to. This will be helpful while querying for the right API.

get_list_of_sectors()

Value

character vector of sectors

Examples

get_list_of_sectors()
